<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.8">
<l>ciṟuviral kaḷtaṭa vippari māṟac</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṅkaṇkō ṭacceyya vāykop paḷippa</l>
<l>kuṟuve yarppuru vamkūṭa lippak</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvintaṉ kuḻalko ṭūtiṉa pōtu</l>
<l>paṟavai yiṉkaṇaṅ kaḷkūṭu tuṟantu</l>
<l rend="indent">vantucūḻn tupaṭu kāṭuki ṭappa</l>
<l>kaṟavai yiṉkaṇaṅ kaḷkālparap piṭṭuk</l>
<l rend="indent">kaviḻntiṟaṅ kiccevi yāṭṭakil lāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When Govinda played [his] flute,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] little fingers pressing down to play,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] red eyes curving,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] red lips pursed,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] brow overhung with beads of sweat,</l>
<l>Groups of birds leaving [their] nests, come circling,</l>
<l rend="indent">descending to settle in the big forest,</l>
<l>[and] herds of milk cows stretch [their] legs,</l>
<l rend="indent">bow [their] heads, and settle down</l>
<l rend="indent">[such that] even [their] ears do not twitch.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
